{
  "texts": [
    "CC-Stories filters out text with a story-like style following the Winograd Schema (Levesque et al, 2012) for common-sense reasoning and language modeling.",
    "RealNews (Zellers et al, 2019b) extracts a substantial amount of webpages dedicated to news to obtain news data.",
    "The above corpora either exclusively contain English or belong to multilingual mixes.",
    "Corpus2020 (Xu et al, 2020c) conducts data cleaning on the Chinese portion of Common Crawl, resulting in a high-quality Chinese pre-training corpus of 100GB.",
    "However, there still exists a small amount of noise in these corpora."
  ]
}